Advection equation with the upstream scheme
===========================================

1. Compiling and running
------------------------

Use the script with

	./run.sh
	

2. Visualizing results in RStudio
---------------------------------

Set working directory with

	setwd('H:\numtech\adveq\')

Load plotting functions with

	source('show.R')

Animate results with

	animateResults('upstream/output.dat')
	
Plot results on a single time step with

	plotResults('upstream/output.dat',timestep=20)